{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"984763b260","title":"吴奔星对人民日报社论的意见","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"aa8056c403","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":11,"articleId":"984763b260"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"582c7dd785","name":"南京师范学院"},{"id":"836aaabd70","name":"吴奔星"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5b35729262","type":"title","text":"吴奔星对人民日报社论的意见","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"984763b260"},{"id":"4a62e44647","type":"authors","text":"南京师范学院吴奔星","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"984763b260"},{"id":"dcdecdb025","type":"subtitle","text":"(吴奔星：南京师范学院中文系教授)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"984763b260"},{"id":"2ba34b3c5d","type":"subtitle","text":"在九三学社南京分社委员、支社委员与部分部门委员座谈会上的讲话","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"984763b260"},{"id":"7d1ae01cfd","type":"paragraph","text":"(一)我们提意见，是为了争取党更好的领导我们，整风要我们和风细雨提意见，但反批评却是狂风暴雨。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"984763b260"},{"id":"dd3773bbbf","type":"paragraph","text":"(二)人民日报社论作用很大，关住了暴露反革命分子的门。这样下去，整风将是虎头蛇尾。真正帮助党整风的人，不敢讲话了。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"984763b260"},{"id":"559c71cdc6","type":"paragraph","text":"(三)匿名信，不可怕。工人发言很好，但人民日报发社论是否有必要？如果问，谁关整风之门，我看，首先就是人民日报。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"984763b260"},{"id":"3d43c1f2a1","type":"paragraph","text":"(四)储安平提毛主席周总理的意见，很好，但态度不够严肃。我们从“大、小和尚”的字眼来挑剔、来责难储，我看没有必要。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"984763b260"},{"id":"e910808adf","type":"paragraph","text":"我们长的不是玻璃脑袋，虽然我们是如此热爱党与毛主席，希望领导上用X光的视线来看我们。人民日报的社论，的确使人感到春天已去，而是“秋风起兮云飞扬”的季节了。但我想，社论只是代表一部分党员，绝不是代表毛主席与周总理的态度。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"984763b260"},{"id":"4b8826540e","type":"paragraph","text":" (转载自新华日报第四号“参考”)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"984763b260"},{"id":"a564137348","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：1957年6月15日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"984763b260"}],"page":{"id":"f1a039c14c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"984763b260","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}